  "texts": [
    "To overcome this limitation, we created long documents by stitching shorter documents from existing datasets.",
    "Each stitched document contains approximately 100 sentences, better reflecting real-world long-document retrieval scenarios.",
    "In this setup, if a short document is relevant to a query, the corresponding stitched long document is considered relevant.",
    "This creates a coarser granularity for document retrieval and motivated the need for the evidence retrieval experiment, which offers a finer level of evaluation.",
    "We selected datasets based on diversity in document topics and query types."
  ],
